<Section id={"section-c"} title={"C. Tool Design"} themeTag={"4 kỹ thuật"}>
  <Fragment is:raw>
    <p>OpenHarness có 42 tools (<code>tools/</code> folder, một file per tool).
    Base class Pydantic đảm bảo type-safety và auto-generate JSON schema cho
    Anthropic/OpenAI SDK. Mỗi tool có truncation giới hạn riêng, bash được bảo
    vệ bằng preflight + PTY, Glob/Grep ưu tiên ripgrep.</p>
  </Fragment>
  <Technique
    id={"t10"}
    title={"T10. Pydantic tool base + auto JSON schema"}
    tid={"C.1"}
    location={"<strong>File:</strong> <code>src/openharness/tools/base.py</code> · <strong>Lines:</strong> 30–52"}
  >
    <Fragment is:raw>
      <h4>Code từ OpenHarness</h4> <pre><code><span class="kw">from</span> abc
      <span class="kw">import</span> ABC, abstractmethod <span class="kw">from
      typing import</span> ClassVar <span class="kw">from</span> pydantic <span
      class="kw">import</span> BaseModel <span class="kw">class</span> <span
      class="type">BaseTool</span>(ABC): name: ClassVar[str] description:
      ClassVar[str] input_model: ClassVar[type[BaseModel]] is_read_only:
      ClassVar[bool] = <span class="kw">False</span> <span
      class="fn">@classmethod</span> <span class="kw">def</span> <span
      class="fn">to_schema</span>(cls) -&gt; dict: <span class="str">"""JSON
      Schema auto-generated from Pydantic input model."""</span> <span
      class="kw">return</span> { <span class="str">"name"</span>: cls.name,
      <span class="str">"description"</span>: cls.description, <span
      class="str">"input_schema"</span>: cls.input_model.model_json_schema(), }
      <span class="fn">@abstractmethod</span> <span class="kw">async def</span>
      <span class="fn">execute</span>(self, args: BaseModel, ctx: ToolContext)
      -&gt; ToolResult: <span class="str">"""Execute tool with validated args;
      return result or error."""</span> ... <span class="com"># Concrete
      usage</span> <span class="kw">class</span> <span
      class="type">ReadInput</span>(BaseModel): file_path: str offset: int |
      <span class="kw">None</span> = <span class="kw">None</span> limit: int |
      <span class="kw">None</span> = <span class="kw">None</span> <span
      class="kw">class</span> <span class="type">ReadTool</span>(BaseTool): name
      = <span class="str">"Read"</span> description = <span class="str">"Read a
      file..."</span> input_model = ReadInput is_read_only = <span
      class="kw">True</span> <span class="kw">async def</span> <span
      class="fn">execute</span>(self, args: ReadInput, ctx) -&gt; ToolResult:
      ...</code></pre> <div class="why"><strong>Tại sao quan trọng:</strong>
      Viết tool Pydantic-first cho 3 lợi ích: (1) <em>validation free</em> —
      args đến tool đã pass schema; (2) <em>JSON schema auto</em> — không cần
      viết tay schema cho mỗi tool (chống drift); (3) <em>IDE friendly</em> —
      tool method có type hints đúng. Hằng <code>is_read_only</code> đặc biệt
      quan trọng: permission checker dùng nó để quyết định có cần confirm hay
      không (read tool luôn OK trong DEFAULT mode).</div> <h4>Code example
      (generic)</h4> <pre><code><span class="kw">from</span> pydantic <span
      class="kw">import</span> BaseModel, Field <span class="kw">from</span> abc
      <span class="kw">import</span> ABC, abstractmethod <span
      class="kw">class</span> <span class="type">BaseTool</span>(ABC): name:
      <span class="type">str</span> input_model: <span
      class="kw">type</span>[BaseModel] <span class="fn">@classmethod</span>
      <span class="kw">def</span> <span class="fn">schema</span>(cls): <span
      class="kw">return</span> {<span class="str">"name"</span>: cls.name, <span
      class="str">"input_schema"</span>: cls.input_model.model_json_schema()}
      <span class="fn">@abstractmethod</span> <span class="kw">async def</span>
      <span class="fn">execute</span>(self, args: BaseModel) -&gt; <span
      class="kw">dict</span>: ... <span class="kw">class</span> <span
      class="type">GrepInput</span>(BaseModel): pattern: <span
      class="type">str</span> = Field(description=<span class="str">"regex
      pattern"</span>) path: <span class="type">str</span> | <span
      class="kw">None</span> = <span class="kw">None</span> <span
      class="kw">class</span> <span class="type">GrepTool</span>(BaseTool): name
      = <span class="str">"Grep"</span> input_model = GrepInput <span
      class="kw">async def</span> <span class="fn">execute</span>(self, args:
      GrepInput): <span class="kw">return</span> <span class="kw">await</span>
      run_ripgrep(args.pattern, args.path)</code></pre>
    </Fragment>
    <ProsCons
      pros={[
        "Single-source-of-truth schema (model_json_schema)",
        "Validation errors có chất lượng cao của Pydantic",
        "mypy strict chấp nhận mọi path",
        "Field descriptions vào docstring LLM-readable",
      ]}
      cons={[
        "Pydantic v2 còn đầu jump từ v1 (breaking changes)",
        "JSON schema đôi khi generate quá phức tạp (Union types), confuse model",
        "Không có cơ chế <code>description_template</code> như opencode .txt",
        "Overhead minor cho mỗi validation call",
      ]}
    />
